<h2 style="color: #333333; margin-bottom: 20px;">Password Reset Request</h2>

<p>Hi <%= userName %>,</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 25px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
  <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666666;">
    This link will expire in <%= expirationTime %>
  </p>
</div>

<div style="margin: 30px 0;">
  <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
  <p style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">
    <%- resetUrl %>
  </p>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #fee2e2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #dc2626;">ðŸ”’ Security Tips:</h4>
  <ul style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #dc2626;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Never share your password with anyone</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Create a strong, unique password</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Enable two-factor authentication when available</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666666;">
  If you didn't request a password reset, please contact our support team immediately. 
  This could indicate someone is trying to access your account without permission.
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #666666;">
  For security reasons, this password reset link will expire in <%- expirationTime %>. 
  After that, you'll need to request a new password reset.
</p>